					Full Description



		Puma Energy Zambia Plc is a fuel, lubricants and oil products distribution and retail company. The Company's fuel supply, storage and distribution helps to manage businesses and provides direct jobs for local people and enterprise opportunities. It provides storage terminals for traders, wholesalers, oil majors and other customers. The Company focuses on midstream and downstream activities. Its midstream business operations include storage, transportation and marine systems. It owns and operates refining assets. Its downstream business operations include retail, wholesale, business-to-business (B2B), aviation, bunkering, bitumen, liquefied petroleum gas (LPG) and lubricants. Its fuel oil, gasoline, diesel, LPG, aviation fuel, bitumen and lubricants connect communities, countries and industries to global trade networks. The Company operates in approximately 50 countries, including Americas, Africa, Europe and Middle East/Asia Pacific.
» Full Overview of PUMA.LZ







