Company Overview of Puma Energy Zambia PLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Puma Energy Zambia Plc markets and distributes petroleum products and lubricants to business and retail customers in Zambia. The company operates in four segments: Retail, Business to Business, Aviation, and Lubricants. It distributes fuel and lubricants to companies operating in Zambia, as well as fuel to airlines; and owns service stations. The company was formerly known as BP Zambia plc and changed its name to Puma Energy Zambia Plc in June 2011. Puma Energy Zambia Plc is based in Lusaka, Zambia.


Airtel HouseStand No 2375Addis Ababa DrivePO Box 31999Lusaka,  Zambia



Phone: 260 2 1137 6100

Fax: 260 2 1137 6149

www.pumaenergy.com







